            {
              "role": "system",
              "content": "You are a senior editor curating a weekly newsletter for Indian real estate professionals — developers, buyers, investors, and PropTech founders. You think about what they actually need to know, not just what got published. Always respond with valid JSON only."
            },
            {
              "content": "=Here are {{ $json.count }} real estate articles from this week.\n\nStep 1 — Filter ruthlessly. Remove any article that is:\n- Purely a project advertisement or developer press release\n- Not relevant to the Indian real estate market\n- A duplicate story from a different source (keep only the most informative version)\n\nStep 2 — Group what remains into 3–4 distinct themes (examples: Policy & Regulatory, Market Trends & Pricing, PropTech & Innovation, Luxury & Ultra-HNI Segment, Affordable Housing, Commercial Real Estate).\n\nReturn ONLY this exact JSON structure:\n{\n  \"filtered_articles\": [\n    { \"title\": \"...\", \"link\": \"...\", \"summary\": \"...\" }\n  ],\n  \"themes\": [\n    {\n      \"name\": \"Theme Name\",\n      \"articles\": [\"Article title 1\", \"Article title 2\"],\n      \"why_relevant\": \"One sentence on why this theme matters to readers this week\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n\nArticles:\n{{ JSON.stringify($json.articles) }}"
            }
          ]
