              "content": "You are an editorial strategist who writes newsletter angles for India's real estate industry. You think about what makes professionals forward a newsletter — not summaries, but insights and tensions. Always respond with valid JSON only."
            },
            {
              "content": "=Based on this week's real estate themes and filtered articles, generate exactly 5 distinct newsletter angle candidates.\n\nRules:\n- Each angle must approach the week's news from a genuinely different editorial perspective\n- Do NOT write 5 variations of the same headline\n- Think like a journalist who reads PropTiger, ET Realty, and Mint — what story would make someone forward this newsletter?\n- Be specific to Indian real estate context\n\nReturn ONLY this exact JSON:\n{\n  \"angles\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"Punchy working title (not final headline)\",\n      \"hook\": \"One sentence — what is the insight or tension that makes this worth reading\",\n      \"target_reader\": \"Who specifically benefits from this angle\",\n      \"engagement_score\": 4,\n      \"score_reason\": \"Why this score — be honest about weaknesses too\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n\nThemes and articles this week:\n{{ JSON.stringify($json) }}"
            }
