            {
              "role": "system",
              "content": "You are an experienced real estate newsletter writer. Your readers are time-poor Indian real estate professionals who've seen every generic 'market is heating up' opener. You write like a smart person talking to another smart person. Always respond with valid JSON only."
            },
            {
              "content": "=From these 5 angle candidates, pick the ONE strongest based on: timeliness, reader curiosity, and originality. Then write the opening 100 words of that newsletter issue.\n\nWriting rules for the draft:\n- First sentence must earn the second. No 'In today's issue...' intros.\n- Write like a smart person talking to another smart person\n- Ground it in a specific data point or observation from the week's news\n- Do not summarise. Start mid-thought.\n- Keep it specifically relevant to the Indian real estate context\n\nReturn ONLY this exact JSON:\n{\n  \"chosen_angle\": { \"title\": \"...\", \"hook\": \"...\" },\n  \"reason_chosen\": \"2-3 sentences on why this beat the others\",\n  \"draft_opening\": \"The actual 100-word opening paragraph\",\n  \"suggested_subject_line\": \"An email subject line for this issue\",\n  \"all_angles\": [\n    {\n      \"rank\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"...\",\n      \"hook\": \"...\",\n      \"target_reader\": \"...\",\n      \"engagement_score\": 5,\n      \"score_reason\": \"...\",\n      \"status\": \"chosen\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"rank\": 2,\n      \"title\": \"...\",\n      \"hook\": \"...\",\n      \"target_reader\": \"...\",\n      \"engagement_score\": 4,\n      \"score_reason\": \"...\",\n      \"status\": \"rejected\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"rank\": 3,\n      \"title\": \"...\",\n      \"hook\": \"...\",\n      \"target_reader\": \"...\",\n      \"engagement_score\": 3,\n      \"score_reason\": \"...\",\n      \"status\": \"rejected\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"rank\": 4,\n      \"title\": \"...\",\n      \"hook\": \"...\",\n      \"target_reader\": \"...\",\n      \"engagement_score\": 3,\n      \"score_reason\": \"...\",\n      \"status\": \"rejected\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"rank\": 5,\n      \"title\": \"...\",\n      \"hook\": \"...\",\n      \"target_reader\": \"...\",\n      \"engagement_score\": 2,\n      \"score_reason\": \"...\",\n      \"status\": \"rejected\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n\nRank 1 must be the chosen angle. Ranks 2-5 are rejected in descending score order.\n\nAngle candidates:\n{{ JSON.stringify($json) }}"
            }
          ]
